---
/**
 * @file DocsPetFriendly.astro
 * @description Content component for the Pet Friendly project status documentation page.
 */
---

<span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-mapa-clay">
	Documentation: Pet Friendly
</span>
<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-mapa-ink/70 tracking-tight sm:text-5xl font-serif mt-2">
	Pet Friendly
</h1>

<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-mapa-ink/60 italic leading-relaxed font-serif">
	This tool is currently in development and not yet live.
</p>

<div class="mt-10 border-t border-mapa-contour/60 pt-8">
	<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-mapa-ink font-serif mb-4">Project status</h2>
	<p class="font-sans text-sm text-mapa-ink/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
		Pet Friendly is a proposed directory utility aimed at mapping animal-welcoming parks, establishments, and cafes across the Philippines.
	</p>
	<p class="font-sans text-sm text-mapa-ink/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
		Because this tool is currently in development, we have not published feature walkthroughs or usage instructions. We will compile and publish complete documentation here once the initial version is deployed.
	</p>
	<p class="font-sans text-sm text-mapa-ink/90 leading-relaxed mb-6">
		You can follow our progress or contribute ideas on the <a href="https://github.com/Shiiroi/mapaph" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-mapa-green hover:underline">mapaPH GitHub Repository</a>.
	</p>
</div>
